r%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%2C%20which%20has%20ruled%20the%20country%20since%20204%2C%20had%20been%20able%20to%20solve%20the%20jobs%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20underlined%20the%20need%20for%20India%20to%20step%20up%20its%20manufacturing%20game%2C%20and%20admitted%20that%20Mr%20Modi%20had%20%26quot%3Btried%20to%20increase%20(this)%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20his%20flagship%20'Make%20in%20India'%20initiative%20was%20%26quot%3Bgood%2C%20as%20a%20concept%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShare%20of%20manufacturing%20fell%20from%2015.3%20per%20cent%20in%202014%20to%2012.6%20per%20cent%20today.%20This%20is%20the%20lowest%20in%2060%20years.%20I%20am%20not%20blaming%20the%20Prime%20Minister...%20it%20would%20not%20be%20fair%20to%20say%20he%20did%20not%20try.%20'Make%20in%20India'%20was%20a%20good%20idea...%20but%20PM%20Modi%20failed%2C%26quot%3B%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20even%20though%20we%20have%20grown%20(and)%20grown%20fast...%20a%20universal%20problem%20we%20have%20faced%20is%20that%20we%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20tackle%20the%20problem%20of%20unemployment.%20Neither%20the%20UPA%20nor%20today's%20NDA%20government%20has%20given%20a%20clear-cut%20answer%20to%20the%20youth%20of%20this%20country%20about%20employment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExcellent%20companies%20had%20tried%20to%20increase%20production%20but%20failed%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20as%20he%20then%20switched%20tack%2C%20and%20let%20fly%20a%20volley%20of%20jabs%26quot%3B...%20but%20now%20we%20have%20handed%20production%20to%20China...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHolding%20up%20his%20mobile%20phone%20as%20an%20example%2C%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%2C%20as%20a%20country%2C%20have%20failed%20in%20organising%20production.%20We%20have%20handed%20it%20over%20to%20China.%20This%20phone%20is%20not%20'Made%20in%20India'...%20It%20is%20only%20assembled%20in%20India.%20All%20the%20components%20are%20made%20in%20China.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20time%20we%20use%20a%20phone%20or%20wear%20a%20Bangladeshi%20shirt...%20we%20pay%20a%20tax%20to%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20now%20on%20the%20warpath%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20then%20pivoted%20to%20the%20India-China%20border%20issue%2C%20declaring%20Beijing%20is%20now%20%26quot%3Bsitting%20on%20over%204%2C000%20sq%20km%20of%20our%20land%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20claimed%20the%20Army%20had%20contradicted%20the%20government's%20assertion%20-%20that%20no%20land%20had%20been%20surrendered%20to%20China.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Prime%20Minister%20denied%20it%20but%20the%20Army%20contradicted%20him...%20China%20is%20sitting%20on%204%2C000%20sq%20km%20of%20our%20territory...%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FBudgetSession2025%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23BudgetSession2025%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Lok%20Sabha%20LoP%20and%20Congress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20says%20%26quot%3BThe%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20denied%20it%20and%20the%20Army%20has%20contradicted%20the%20Prime%20Minsiter%20that%20China%20is%20sitting%20on%204000%20sq%20km%20of%20our%20territory...%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnLok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20says%20%26quot%3BYou%20will%20have%20to%20present%20the%20evidence%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fu4XswMd2VO%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fu4XswMd2VO%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1886345490339647897%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%203%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%20said%20Chinese%20are%20inside%20our%20territory...%20this%20is%20a%20fact%20(and)%20the%20reason%20China%20is%20inside%20is%20because%20'Make%20in%20India'%20has%20failed