3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20addressing%20a%20public%20rally%20at%20New%20Delhi's%20RK%20Puram%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20that%20similar%20to%20the%20change%20of%20weather%20ushered%20in%20with%20the%20arrival%20of%20Basant%20Panchami%2C%20Delhi%20will%20herald%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%20spring%20of%20development.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20few%20days%2C%20a%20new%20spring%20of%20development%20will%20arrive%20in%20Delhi.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20is%20about%20to%20form%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20'AAP-da%20party'%20has%20wasted%2011%20years.%20My%20biggest%20request%20is%20that%20we%20should%20be%20given%20a%20chance%20to%20serve%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi.%20I%20promise%20to%20go%20to%20any%20length%20to%20remove%20every%20difficulty%20you%20face.%20A%20double-engine%20government%20will%20come%20to%20Delhi%20that%20will%20make%20the%20lives%20of%20every%20poor%20and%20middle-class%20family%20prosperous%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20guaranteed%20Rs%205%20nutritious%20meals%20for%20people%20living%20in%20slums%20and%20announced%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20a%20welfare%20board%20for%20auto%20drivers%20and%20domestic%20workers%2C%20while%20assuring%20that%20no%20existing%20welfare%20schemes%20would%20be%20discontinued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20welfare%20board%20will%20be%20set%20up%20for%20auto%20drivers%20and%20domestic%20workers%2C%20providing%20them%20with%20insurance%20coverage%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%20The%20BJP%20government%20will%20also%20assist%20with%20children's%20school%20fees.%20I%20give%20another%20guarantee%3A%20these%20AAP-Da%20people%20are%20spreading%20falsehoods%2C%20but%20not%20a%20single%20slum%20in%20Delhi%20will%20be%20demolished.%20The%20welfare%20schemes%20for%20the%20public%20in%20Delhi%20will%20not%20be%20stopped%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Assembly%20elections%20will%20take%20place%20on%20February%205%20in%20a%20single%20phase%2C%20