r%20he%20should%20recuse%20from%20the%20hearing%20as%20he%20attended%20a%20dinner%20hosted%20by%20the%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%20when%20he%20was%20elevated%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20the%20petitioner's%20lawyer%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20said%20Justice%20Kumar%20need%20not%20recuse%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20problem%2C%20not%20one%20bit%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhushan%20told%20the%20two-judge%20bench%20also%20comprising%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20Sanjiv%20Khanna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhushan%2C%20who%20represented%20the%20petitioner%2C%20Kuki%20Organisation%20for%20Human%20Rights%20Trust%20(KOHUR)%2C%20said%20the%20non-profit%20Truth%20Labs%20confirmed%20that%2093%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20audio%20tapes%20matched%20Mr%20Singh's%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETruth%20Labs%2C%20set%20up%20in%202007%2C%20is%20India's%20first%20non-government%20full-fledged%20forensic%20lab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20of%20India%20Tushar%20Mehta%20said%20the%20report%20of%20Truth%20Labs%20cannot%20be%20relied%20on.%20The%20audio%20clips%20have%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20Central%20Forensic%20Science%20Laboratory%20(CFSL)%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTruth%20Labs%20reports%20are%20far%20more%20reliable%20than%20CFSL%20reports%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhushan%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20hearing%20the%20submissions%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20sought%20a%20report%20from%20the%20CFSL%20in%20a%20sealed%20cover%20and%20listed%20the%20matter%20for%20hearing%20again%20in%20the%20week%20beginning%20March%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20the%20veracity%20of%20the%20transcript%20also...%20When%20will%20the%20CFSL%20report%20come%3F%20Let%20it%20be%20examined.%20Let%20it%20not%20become%20another%20issue.%20File%20a%20report%20within%20one%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20Khanna%20told%20the%20Solicitor%20General.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20state%20is%20limping%20back%20now.%20We%20have%20to%20also%20see%20if%20this%20court%20should%20hear%20this%20matter%20or%20the%20high%20court%20should%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20Khanna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhushan%20said%20the%20audio%20clips%20were%20recorded%20by%20a%20person%20during%20a%20closed-door%20meeting%20with%20the%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%2C%20Mr%20Mehta%20replied%20the%20investigators%20have%20approached%20the%20person%20who%20uploaded%20the%20audio%20clips%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20also%20another%20issue...%20The%20petitioner%20carries%20a%20baggage%20and%20has%20ideological%20inclinations%2C%20separatists%20sorts...%20There%20is%20a%20report%20by%20the%20three-judge%20committee%20about%20wanting%20to%20keep%20the%20pot%20boiling%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Solicitor%20General%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20Supreme%20Court-appointed%20committee%20headed%20by%20former%20high%20court%20judge%20Justice%20Gita%20Mittal%20on%20the%20Manipur%20crisis%2C%20which%20in%20November%202023%20flagged%20actions%20by%20civil%20society%20groups%20as%20destabilising.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-03%2F188kmta8_hs-benjamin-mate-_625x300_11_March_19.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHS%20Benjamin%20Mate%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHS%20Benjamin%20Mate%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20petitioner%20KOHUR%2C%20is%20also%20a%20top%20leader%20of%20another%20body%20called%20Kuki%20Inpi%2C%20which%20endorsed%20the%20demand%20by%20Kuki%20leaders%20and%20militants%20under%20the%20suspension%20of%20operations%20(SoO)%20agreement%20for%20a%20separate%20administration%20carved%20out%20of%20Manipur.%C2%A0His%20organisation%20has%20alleged%20the%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20has%20been%20harassing%20him%20to%20force%20him%20into%20silence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMHA%20Commission%20Of%20Inquiry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Commission%20of%20Inquiry%20formed%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20is%20looking%20into%20the%20purported%20audio%20tapes.%20The%20people%20who%20submitted%20the%20tapes%20have%20given%20sworn%20affidavits%20that%20the%20tapes%20were%20genuine%2C%20the%20news%20website%20The%20Wire%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki%20Students'%20Organisation%20(KSO)%20first%20released%20a%20part%20of%20the%20audio%20clip%20on%20August%207%2C%202024%2C%20and%20another%20on%20August%2020%2C%20when%20The%20Wire%20reported%20about%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20case%20reached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20KSO%20in%20a%20statement%20had%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20shocked%20and%20outraged%20by%20the%20continued%20inaction%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India%20regarding%20the%20leaked%20audio%20recording%20of%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Bid%20To%20Derail%20Peace%20Talks'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20government%20called%20the%20tapes%20%26quot%3Bdoctored%26quot%3B%20to%20derail%20any%20peace%20process%20in%20the%20ethnic%20violence-hit%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20This%20doctored%20audio%20is%20a%20malicious%20attempt%20by%20certain%20sections%20to%20incite%20communal%20violence%20or%20to%20derail%20the%20process%20of%20peace%20that%20has%20been%20initiated%20at%20multiple%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20state%20government%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20August%207%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20Congress%20vice%20president%20Lamtinthang%20Haokip%20was%20among%20those%20who%20posted%20the%20purported%20audio%20clips%20that%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20government%20termed%20as%20%26quot%3Bdoctored%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETen%20Kuki-Zo%20MLAs%20who%20have%20been%20demanding%20a%20separate%20administration%20also%20requested%20the%20MHA%20Commission%20of%20Inquiry%20to%20expedite%20looking%20into%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20complicity%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20in%20the%20state-sponsored%20ethnic%20cleansing%2C%20which%20we%20have%20always%20maintained%20since%20day%20one%2C%20has%20now%20been%20established%20beyond%20an%20iota%20of%20doubt...%26quot%3B%20they%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20August%2022%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20repeatedly%20said%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20began%20as%20a%20pushback%20by%20%26quot%3Bnarcoterrorists%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20state%20government's%20'War%20on%20Drugs'%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Ftbk522t8_manipur-illegal-immigrants_625x300_02_May_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIllegal%20immigrants%20from%20neighbouring%20Myanmar%20deported%20from%20Manipur%20(file)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Meitei%20community%20has%20alleged%20decades%20of%20the%20open-border%20policy%20with%20Myanmar%20have%20backfired%2C%20with%20illegal%20immigrants%20settling%20down%20and%20raising%20hundreds%20of%20new%20villages%20to%20call%20them%20ancestral%20land%20in%20due%20time.%20The%20Kuki%20tribes%20also%20follow%20the%20hereditary%20chieftainship%20system%2C%20under%20which%20village%20chiefs%20own%20massive%20tracts%20of%20land.%20Neighbouring%20Mizoram%20scrapped%20the%20chieftainship%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20of%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20have%20refuted%20allegations%20the%20tribes%20have%20been%20sheltering%20illegal%20immigrants%20for%20demographic%20engineering.%20They%20have%20said%20powerful%20people%20in%20the%20valley%20want%20to%20grab%20their%20lands%2C%20and%20so%20made%20up%20the%20illegal%20immigrants%20story%20to%20scare%20people%20into%20becoming%20hostile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clashes%20between%20the%20valley-dominant%20Meitei%20community%20and%20over%20a%20dozen%20distinct%20tribes%20collectively%20known%20as%20Kuki%2C%20who%20are%20dominant%20in%20some%20hill%20areas%20of%20Manipur%2C%20have%20killed%20over%20250%20people%20and%20internally%20displaced%20nearly%2050%2C000.%20There%20are%20many%20villages%20of%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20in%20the%20hills%20surrounding%20the%20valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20general%20category%20Meiteis%20want%20to%20be%20included%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20category%2C%20while%20the%20Kukis%20who%20share%20ethnic%20ties%20with%20people%20in%20neighbouring%20Myanmar's%20Chin%20State%20and%20Mizoram%20want%20a%20separate%20administration%20carved%20out%20of%20Manipur%2C%20citing%20discrimination%20and%20unequal%20share%20of%20resources%20and%20power%20with%20the%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738573260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Frsc39d6g_n-biren-singh_625x300_17_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-seeks-government-forensic-report-on-audio-clips-purportedly-of-manipur-chief-minister-instigating-violence-7622172%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20sought%20a%20report%20from%20the%20government%20forensic%20laboratory%20CFSL%20on%20leaked%20audio%20tapes%20purportedly%20of%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20who%20a%20petitioner%20of%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20alleged%20instigated%20the%20Manipur%20violence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-seeks-government-forensic-report-on-audio-clips-purportedly-of-manipur-chief-minister-instigating-violence-7622172%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vivo%20V50%20smartphone%20with%20Zeiss%20camera%20launching%20soon%3A%20Expected%20specs%2C%20more%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1