.%20Last%20February%2C%20he%20landed%20an%20offer%20from%20JPMorgan%20that%20would%20require%20him%20to%20work%20from%20the%20office%20three%20days%20a%20week%20in%20Manhattan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20mulled%20over%20the%20offer%2C%20he%20estimated%20that%20his%20commuting%20time%20would%20total%20nine%20hours%20a%20week%20%E2%80%94%20or%20roughly%20450%20hours%20a%20year.%20Parking%20at%20his%20local%20train%20stain%20and%20taking%20the%20New%20Jersey%20Transit%20would%20cost%20him%20roughly%20%247%2C200%20in%20annual%20commuting%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Steven%20received%20another%20job%20offer%20%E2%80%94%20this%20one%20for%20a%20remote%20position%20that%20offered%20an%20annual%20salary%20that%20was%20around%20%245%2C000%20lower%20than%20the%20JPMorgan%20role.%20When%20he%20compared%20the%20jobs%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20money%20he'd%20earn%20for%20every%20hour%20he'd%20have%20to%20%26quot%3Binvest%26quot%3B%20in%20them%20%E2%80%94%20including%20commuting%20time%20%E2%80%94%20he%20said%20it%20was%20an%20easy%20choice%20to%20pick%20the%20remote%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJPMorgan%20just%20could%20not%20compete%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BA%2040-hour%20week%20plus%20nine%20commute%20hours%20is%20basically%20a%2050-hour%20week%20for%20the%20salary%20that%20they%20were%20offering.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteven%20said%20he's%20particularly%20grateful%20he%20turned%20down%20the%20offer%20because%2C%20on%20January%2010%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-return-to-office-memo-ending-remote-work-jamie-dimon-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJPMorgan%20announced%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20most%20employees%20would%20be%20required%20to%20work%20from%20the%20office%20five%20days%20a%20week%20beginning%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Richard%20is%20still%20looking%20for%20a%20remote%20role%20while%20commuting%20to%20his%20current%20job.%20Due%20to%20space%