t%20-%20which%2C%20for%20hours%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20refused%20to%20confirm%20fatalities%20-%20is%20hiding%20the%20actual%20number%20of%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20called%20for%20order%2C%20and%20accused%20the%20opposition%20of%20not%20wanting%20the%20House%20to%20function.%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20also%20made%20an%20appeal%20to%20the%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20shared%20by%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20Mr%20Birla%20called%20out%20one%20of%20the%20protesting%20politicians%20-%20Pradyut%20Bordoloi%2C%20the%20Congress%20MP%20from%20Assam's%20Nowgong%20seat%20-%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20people%20sent%20you%20to%20Parliament%20to%20ask%20questions..%20not%20break%20tables.%20If%20that%20is%20what%20you%20want%20to%20do%2C%20then%20hit%20it%20harder...%20break%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Speaker%20then%20invited%20Alok%20Sharma%2C%20a%20BJP%20MP%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20to%20ask%20his%20question%2C%20even%20as%20the%20sloganeering%20and%20shouting%20continues%3B%20a%20disgruntled%20Mr%20Birla%20also%20took%20off%20his%20headset.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20also%20kicked%20up%20a%20fuss%20on%20this%20issue.%20The%20Congress'%20Pramod%20Tiwari%20told%20reporters%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20walked%20out%20for%20an%20hour.%20We%20will%20go%20back%20again%20and%20raise%20this%20issue.%20We%20are%20getting%20calls...people%20are%20not%20able%20to%20meet%20families.%20We%20want%20to%20know%20why%20the%20list%20of%2030%20dead%20has%20not%20been%20released.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20foreshadowing%20of%20this%20morning's%20chaos%20was%20felt%20last%20week%3B%20on%20Saturday%20too%20there%20was%20sloganeering%20and%20(a%20small%20amount%20of)%20disorder%20as%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20was%20reading%20out%20the%20Union%20Budget%202025.%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20and%20his%20Samajwadi%20Party%20led%20that%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstro