20Trump%20to%20retain%20PEPFAR%2C%20a%20long-running%20foreign%20aid%20program%20that%20combats%20HIV.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20halting%20all%20foreign%20aid%20programs%20for%2090%20days%20after%20he%20was%20sworn%20in.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gates%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBill%20Gates%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he%20pushed%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20maintain%20America's%20aid%20and%20relief%20programs%20for%20HIV%20during%20a%20meeting%20they%20had%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGates%20told%20The%20New%20Yorker's%20editor%20David%20Remnick%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newyorker.com%2Fpodcast%2Fthe-new-yorker-radio-hour%2Fbill-gates-on-his-new-memoir-and-dining-with-donald-trump-at-mar-a-lago%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20Sunday%2C%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bhad%20a%20really%20good%2C%20very%20long%20dinner%26quot%3B%20with%20Trump%20at%20Mar-a-Lago%20after%20Christmas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWell%2C%20we%20talked%20about%20the%20world%20broadly%2C%20but%20my%20first%20request%20was%20on%20HIV%2C%20where%20there's%20a%20question%20of%20whether%20the%20US%20maintains%20the%20PEPFAR%20program%20that's%20over%20twenty%20years%20standing%2C%20that%20keeps%20over%20ten%20million%20people%20alive%20with%20HIV%20medicines%2C%26quot%3B%20Gates%20told%20Remnick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPEPFAR%2C%20or%20the%20President's%20Emergency%20Plan%20for%20AIDS%20Relief%2C%20is%20a%20foreign%20aid%20program%20that%20was%20started%20by%20then-President%20George%20W.%20Bush%20in%202003.%20The%20program%20has%20saved%2026%20million%20lives%20and%20prevented%20millions%20of%20HIV%20infections%20around%20the%20world%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Fpepfar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EState%20Department%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20funding%20for%20PEPFAR%20was%20paused%20on%20January%2020%2C%20after%20Trump%20signed%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fpresidential-actions%2F2025%2F01%2Freevaluating-and-realigning-united-states-foreign-aid%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexecutive%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20freezing%20all%20foreign%20aid%20programs%20for%2090%20days%20until%20they%20are%20reviewed.%20According%20to%20the%20State%20Department%2C%20the%20US%20has%20given%20over%20%24110%20billion%20in%20funding%20to%20PEPFAR.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20his%20ear%20for%20three%20hours.%20He%20couldn't%20have%20been%20nicer.%20Doesn't%20mean%20that%20other%20people%20won't%20come%20in%20and%20say%20the%20HIV%20money%20should%20be%20cut%2C%20but%20I%20did%20my%20best%2C%26quot%3B%20Gates%20said%20of%20his%20meeting%20with%20Trump%20in%20his%20interview%20with%20The%20New%20Yorker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unclear%20what%20will%20become%20of%20PEPFAR%20under%20Trump.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20announced%20a%20waiver%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Femergency-humanitarian-waiver-to-foreign-assistance-pause%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efor%20life-saving%20humanitarian%20assistance%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20to%20Trump's%20executive%20order%20on%20foreign%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20resumption%20is%20temporary%20in%20nature%2C%20and%20with%20limited%20exceptions%20as%20needed%20to%20continue%20life-saving%20humanitarian%20assistance%20programs%2C%20no%20new%20contracts%20shall%20be%20entered%20into%2C%26quot%3B%20Rubio%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Femergency-humanitarian-waiver-to-foreign-assistance-pause-2%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGates%20has%20given%20money%20to%20philanthropi