he%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20Delhi.%20Targeting%20the%20ruling%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20Mr%20Naidu%20said%20the%20Delhi%20government%20model%20has%20%26quot%3Bfailed%26quot%3B%20and%20people%20should%20vote%20for%20a%20party%20that%20can%20lead%20to%20inclusive%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPoliticians%20have%20to%20always%20think%20about%20today%2C%20tomorrow%20and%20the%20future.%20A%20government%20with%20good%20public%20policy%20can%20transform%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20describing%20the%20AAP%20government%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bhalf-engine%20sarkar%26quot%3B.%20Delhi%2C%20he%20said%2C%20needs%20a%20double-engine%20government.%20Double-engine%20government%20is%20a%20term%20the%20BJP%20uses%20in%20Assembly%20poll%20campaigns%20to%20stress%20that%20the%20BJP%20in%20power%20at%20both%20the%20state%20and%20Centre%20levels%20would%20ensure%20all-round%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Naidu%20said%20people%20are%20now%20worried%20about%20staying%20in%20Delhi%20because%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bweather%20and%20political%20pollution%26quot%3B.%20Performance%20and%20better%20living%20standards%20are%20becoming%20more%20relevant%20now%20than%20ideology%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bpoor%20people%20in%20Delhi%20would%20have%20to%20think%20if%20they%20want%20to%20live%20permanently%20in%20slums%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Budget%202025%2C%20he%20said%20TDP%20fully%20supports%20the%20Budget%20proposals%20because%20they%20aim%20to%20achieve%20the%20goal%20of%20Viksit%20Bharat%20by%202047.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20agreement%20with%20them.%20We%20are%20happy.%20It%20syncs%20with%20our%2010%20principles%20of%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Mr%20Naidu%20had%20thanked%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20for%20presenting%20a%20%26quot%3Bpro-people%20and%20progressive%20budget%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThis%20budget%20reflects%20the%20vision%20for%20a%20Viksit%20Bharat%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Hon'ble%20Prime%20Minister%20Shri%20%40narendramodi%20Ji.%20It%20prioritises%20the%20welfare%20of%20women%2C%20the%20poor%2C%20youth%2C%20and%20farmers%2C%20while%20also%20identifying%20six%20key%20sectors%20for%20growth%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years.%20The%20budget%20marks%20a%20significant%20step%20towards%20national%20prosperity.%20It%20serves%20as%20a%20comprehensive%20and%20inclusive%20blueprint%2C%20promising%20a%20prosperous%20future%20for%20our%20country.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20brings%20tax%20relief%20for%20the%20middle%20class%2C%20the%20backbone%20of%20our%20country's%20economy.%20I%20welcome%20this%20budget.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Naidu's%20TDP%20is%20the%20BJP's%20key%20ally%20at%20the%20Centre.%20Its%2016%20MPs%2C%20along%20with%20the%20JDU's%2012%2C%20helped%20the%20BJP%20form%20the%20government%20after%20it%20fell%20short%20of%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20general%20election%20last%20year.%20But%20while%20Bihar%20got%20several%20gifts%20in%20this%20Budget%2C%20expected%20because%20state%20polls%20are%20due%20there%2C%20there%20were%20no%20big%20announcements%20for%20Andhra.%20This%20prompted%20the%20Congress%20and%20TDP's%20arch-rival%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%20to%20take%20swipes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBihar%20appears%20to%20have%20got%20a%20bonanza%20of%20announcements.%20It%20is%20natural%20since%20elections%20are%20due%20there%20later%20in%20the%20year.%20But%20why%20has%20the%20other%20pillar%20of%20the%20NDA%2C%20namely%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20been%20so%20cruelly%20ignored%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20YS%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy-led%20YSR%20Congress%20said%20Mr%20Naidu%20failed%20to%20secure%20Andhra's%20due%20share.%20Senior%20party%20leader%20B%20Rajendranath%20Reddy%20said%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20%26quot%3Bfailed%26quot%3B%20to%20mount%20pressure%20on%20the%20Centre%20to%20secure%20more%20for%20Andhra%20and%20the%20advanta