et%20aims%20to%20achieve%20goal%20of%20Viksit%20Bharat%20by%202047%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-election-budget-2025-chandrababu-naidus-arvind-kejriwal-jagan-reddy-parallel-at-delhi-poll-rally-7621935%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20Tariffs%20Offset%20Budget%20Boost%2C%20Rupee%20Hits%20Record%20Low%2C%20Markets%20Crash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEquity%20benchmark%20indices%20Sensex%20and%20Nifty%20tumbled%20in%20early%20trade%20and%20the%20rupee%20hit%20a%20record%20low%20of%2087.29%20against%20the%20US%20dollar%20on%20Monday%20after%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20imposed%20massive%20tariffs%20on%20Canada%2C%20China%20and%20Mexico%20over%20the%20weekend%2C%20sparking%20fears%20of%20a%20broader%20trade%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSE%20Sensex%20was%20down%20by%20more%20than%20400%20points%20to%2077%2C084%20at%2011%20am%2C%20while%20the%20Nifty%2050%20dropped%20to%2023%2C320%20after%20losing%20over%20160%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELarsen%20%26amp%3B%20Toubro%2C%20NTPC%2C%20Tata%20Steel%2C%20Power%20Grid%2C%20Tata%20Motors%2C%20Reliance%20Industries%2C%20ICICI%20Bank%20and%20Tata%20Consultancy%20Services%20were%20among%20the%20major%20laggards%20from%20the%2030-share%20blue-chip%20pack%2C%20while%20Titan%2C%20Maruti%2C%20Nestle%20and%20Bajaj%20Finserv%20were%20among%20the%20gainers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20an%20excellent%20Budget%2C%20the%20market%20will%20be%20under%20pressure%20from%20the%20Trump%20tariffs%20and%20the%20heightened%20global%20uncertainty%20these%20'initial%20round%20of%20tariffs'%20has%20triggered%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20news%20agency%20PTI%20quoted%20VK%20Vijayakumar%2C%20the%20Chief%20Investment%20Strategist%20at%20the%20Geojit%20Financial%20Services%2C%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikram%20Kasat%2C%20the%20head%20of%20advisory%20of%20PL%20Capital%20of%20Prabhudas%20Lilladher%2C%20said%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bshock%26quot%3B%20among%20investors%20after%20Trump%20followed%20through%20on%20his%20threat%20to%20hit%20the%20three%20countries%20with%20tariffs%20on%20imports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20near-term%20market%20trajectory%20will%20depend%20on%20%26quot%3Bhow%20investors%20react%20to%20something%20that%20is%20almost%20universally%20damaging%20for%20economic%20growth%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20Asian%20markets%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20Hong%20Kong%20were%20also%20trading%20sharply%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERupee%20Drops%20To%20Record%20Low%20After%20Trump's%20Tariffs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rupee%20continued%20to%20face%20pressure%20due%20to%20sustained%20foreign%20fund%20outflows%20and%20weakened%20past%2087%20to%20the%20US%20dollar%20for%20the%20first%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20dropped%20to%20an%20all-time%20low%20of%2087.1450%20per%20dollar%2C%20down%200.6%25%20from%20Friday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rupee's%20losses%20are%20now%20approaching%204%25%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20October%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20Asian%20currencies%20also%20tumbled%20with%20the%20Korean%20won%2C%20Malaysian%20ringgit%2C%20Indonesian%20rupiah%20and%20Thai%20baht%20dropping%200.9%25%20to%201.2%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDonald%20Trump%20Sparks%20Trade%20War%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20on%20Saturday%20slapped%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20with%2025%20per%20cent%20duties%20and%20China%20with%20a%2010%20per%20cent%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20protect%20Americans%2C%20and%20it%20is%20my%20duty%20as%20President%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20all.%20I%20made%20a%20promise%20on%20my%20campaign%20to%20stop%20the%20flood%20of%20illegal%20aliens%20and%20drugs%20from%20pouring%20across%20our%20borders%2C%20and%20Americans%20overwhelmingly%20voted%20in%20favor%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20on%20social%20media%20after%20signing%20three%20separate%20executive%20orders%20on%20the%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2078-year-old%2C%20who%20has%20launched%20numerous%20tariff%20threats%20upon%20returning%20to%20office%2C%20later%20said%20that%20Americans%20may%20feel%20economic%20%26quot%3Bpain%26quot%3B%20from%20his%20tariffs%20on%20key%20trading%20partners%2C%20but%20argued%20it%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bworth%20the%20price%26quot%3B%20to%20secure%20US%20interests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWill%20there%20be%20some%20pain%3F%20Yes%2C%20maybe%20(and%20maybe%20not!)%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20his%20Truth%20Social%20media%20platform%20on%20Sunday.%20%26quot%3BBut%20we%20will%20Make%20America%20Great%20Again%2C%20and%20it%20will%20all%20be%20worth%20the%20price%20that%20must%20be%20paid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECanada%2C%20Mexico%2C%20China%20Respond%20To%20Trump%20Tariffs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20announced%2025%20per%20cent%20retaliatory%20tariffs%20against%20Can%24155%20billion%20(%24106%20billion)%20worth%20of%20American%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMexican%20President%20Claudia%20Sheinbaum%20Pardo%20also%20shot%20back%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3Bthe%20problems%20are%20not%20resolved%20by%20imposing%20tariffs%2C%20but%20by%20talking%20and%20dialoguing%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20instruct%20the%20Secretary%20of%20Economy%20to%20implement%20Plan%20B%20that%20we%20have%20been%20working%20on%2C%20which%20includes%20tariff%20and%20non-tariff%20measures%20in%20defense%20of%20Mexico's%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20said%20it%20would%20challenge%20Trump's%20levies%20at%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20on%20Sunday%20reiterated%20to%20place%20new%20tariffs%20on%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20saying%20they%20have%20%26quot%3Breally%20taken%20advantage%2