_blank%5C%22%3EDeep%20research%20in%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20new%20agentic%20capability%20that%20conducts%20multi-step%20research%20on%20the%20internet%20for%20complex%20tasks%20and%20accomplishes%20in%20tens%20of%20minutes%20what%20would%20take%20a%20human%20many%20hours%2C%20OpenAI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeep%20research%20is%20OpenAI's%20next%20agent%20that%20can%20do%20work%20for%20you%20independently-you%20give%20it%20a%20prompt%2C%20and%20ChatGPT%20will%20find%2C%20analyze%2C%20and%20synthesize%20hundreds%20of%20online%20sources%20to%20create%20a%20comprehensive%20report%20at%20the%20level%20of%20a%20research%20analyst%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPowered%20by%20a%20version%20of%20the%20upcoming%20OpenAI%20o3%20model%20that's%20optimized%20for%20web%20browsing%20and%20data%20analysis%2C%20the%20company%20said%20the%20deep%20research%20is%20built%20for%20people%20who%20do%20intensive%20knowledge%20work%20in%20areas%20like%20finance%2C%20science%2C%20policy%2C%20and%20engineering%20and%20need%20thorough%2C%20precise%2C%20and%20reliable%20research.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20be%20equally%20useful%20for%20discerning%20shoppers%20looking%20for%20hyper-personalized%20recommendations%20on%20purchases%20that%20typically%20require%20careful%20research%2C%20like%20cars%2C%20appliances%2C%20and%20furniture%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20To%20Use%20'Deep%20Research'%20Tool%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20use%20OpenAI's%20new%20tool%2C%20select%20'deep%20research'%20in%20the%20message%20composer%20in%20ChatGPT%20and%20enter%20your%20question.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20attach%20files%20or%20spreadsheets%20to%20add%20context%20to%20your%20query.%20Once%20it%20starts%20running%2C%20a%20sidebar%20appears%20with%20a%20summary%20of%20the%20steps%20taken%20and%20sources%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tool%20may%20take%20anywhere%20from%20about%205%20to%2030%20minutes%20to%20complete%20its%20work%20and%20you%20will%20get%20a%20notification%20once%20the%20research%20is%20complete.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20said%20that%20in%20the%20next%20few%20weeks%2C%20they%20will%20also%20add%20embedded%20images%2C%20data%20visualisations%2C%20and%20other%20analytic%20outputs%20in%20these%20reports%20for%20additional%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Deep%20Research'%20Launched%20Amid%20DeepSeek%20Buzz%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20new%20tool%20has%20been%20launched%20amid%20a%20buzz%20over%20the%20AI%20chatbot%20developed%20by%20Chinese%20start-up%20DeepSeek%2C%20which%20has%20sent%20shockwaves%20through%20the%20industry%20for%20its%20R1%20chatbot's%20supposed%20low%20cost%20and%20high%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunched%20last%20month%2C%20DeepSeek-R1%20is%2020%20to%2050%20times%20more%20affordable%20to%20use%20than%20OpenAI's%20o1%20model%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20task%2C%20according%20to%20a%20post%20on%20DeepSeek's%20official%20WeChat%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepSeek's%20free%20AI%20assistant%20had%20last%20week%20overtaken%20ChatGPT%20in%20downloads%20from%20Apple's%20app%20store%2C%20hitting%20shares%20of%20several%20big%20tech%20players%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-lost-who-won-after-selloff-linked-to-deepseek-slams-markets-7576588%5C%22%3ENvidia%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdeepseeks-r1-is-an-impressive-model-says-openai-chief-sam-altman-7575749%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20called%20its%20R1%20AI%20model%20%26quot%3Bimpressive%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738559040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Feha464n_openai_625x300_03_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fndtv-explainer-what-is-openais-deep-research-tool-