cklash%20on%20Russian%20social%20media%20toward%20the%20treatment%20of%20the%20war's%20wounded%2C%20after%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fbelarusian_silovik%2F48058%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20went%20viral%20in%20mid-January%20showed%20a%20man%20in%20military%20fatigues%20assaulting%20two%20injured%20Russians%20with%20a%20baton%20and%20a%20stun%20gun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocal%20authorities%20in%20Kyzyl%2C%20a%20city%20in%20the%20Russian%20region%20of%20Tuva%2C%20told%20Moscow-based%20news%20agency%20Interfax%20that%20they%20were%20investigating%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20Defense%20Ministry%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20comment%20request%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESigns%20of%20strain%20in%20Russia's%20troop%20supply%20are%20significant%2C%20because%20the%20war%20now%20increasingly%20hinges%20on%20whether%20Moscow%20or%20Kyiv%20can%20outlast%20each%20other%20in%20terms%20of%20gear%20and%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20enlist%20recruits%2C%20the%20Kremlin%20has%20been%20raising%20sign-up%20bonuses%20and%20benefits%20for%20newcomers%2C%20with%20some%20Russian%20regions%20seeing%20cash%20incentives%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-sign-up-bonuses-reaching-on-par-with-us-military-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealmost%20on%20par%20with%20the%20US%20military's.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20is%20already%20set%20to%20spend%20almost%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-economy-federal-budget-putin-record-defense-spending-ukraine-war-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethird%20of%20its%20federal%20budget%20on%20defense%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202025%2C%20or%2013.5%20trillion%20rubles%20(worth%20%24135%20billion%2C%20at%20press%20time)%2C%20as%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-economy-entering-year-of-pain-2025-pu